quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,Hageze aho abantu iharurwa ryabo ry’umusi w’imperuka ryashitse nabo ataco bibuka n’uguhakana gusa
  21,2,Ntabutumwa bushasha buzobashikira buvuye ku Muremyi wabo atari uko babwumva nabo babifata minenegwe
  21,3,"Imitima yabo yaribagijwe nabo bongorerana mumbari bamwe bahemukiye imitima yabo babwirana bati:- uyu Muhammadi (aui) atari uko ari umuntu nkamwe, noneho mwashikiye kuburozi namwe aho muri mwibonera"
  21,4,"Intumwa y’Imana Muhammadi (iii) yavuze iti:- Umuremyi wanje niyo ifise ubumenyi bwibivugirwa mw’Ijuru no kw’Isi, nayo niyo yumva kandi niyo ifise ubumenyi buhagije"
  21,5,"Mugabo abahakanyi b’Imana bavuze bati:- ibi vyose n’indoto zivanganye n’izindi, ahubwo nivyo yigiriye kubwiwe, kandi uyu muntu n’umwanditsi yiyandikira amajambo y’ubuhizi gusa, rero natuzanire ibitangaro nkuko barungitswe izindi ntumwa z’Imana zaho hambere"
  21,6,"Ntibemeye abari imbere yabo aribo banyagihugu baba Qurayshi bo mugisagara icarico twahoneje, mbega aba bantu bazokwemera"
  21,7,"Ntitwaba rungitse imbere yawe atari abagabo twahaye ubutumwa, rero nimubabaze abacibuka nimwaba mwebwe mutabizi"
  21,8,"Natwe ntitwabahaye imibiri idafungura ibifungurwa, kandi ntibari kuba ari abantu bokubaho mubuzima bwabo bwose"
  21,9,"Hanyuma\ttwarabemereye\tamasezerano\tnukubarokora\thamwe\tnabo twishakiye, nuguhonya abamaze kurenga imbibe z’Imana"
  21,10,"Ntankeka twaraba manuriye igitabu, murico harimwo ubutumwa kuri mwebwe, mbega ntimutegera"
  21,11,"N’ibisagara\tbingahe twahoneje\tku bantu bamye bahemukira\timitima yabo, natwe munyuma duca turema abandi bantu"
  21,12,"Mugihe bikeka ibihano vyacu, mumwanya baciye batangura kwiruka"
  21,13,Ntimwiruke ahubwo nimugaruke kuvyo mwahora mwinezereza ko mumazu yanyu kugira ngo mubazwe
  21,14,"Nabo bavuga bati:- Oh! mu vy’ukuri twari mubahemukiye imitima yacu"
  21,15,Haca habandanya ivyitwazo vyabo kugeza naho tubagira nk’abatemwe nukuzimwa impwemu zabo nugucikana
  21,16,Ntitwaremye Amajuru n’Isi hamwe n’ibiri hagati nkugufyinata
  21,17,Iyo dushaka gufyinata twari kwigirira twebwe nyene nkiyo tuba dushaka gufyinata
  21,18,"Ahubwo ivyo dushaka kugira nibi:- nuguta ukuri hejuru y’ikinyoma kugaca kumena ifufu ry’umutwe hanyuma ikinyoma kikazimangana, n’ibihano vy’Imana birabarindiriye kubera ibi vyose muvuga"
  21,19,"N’ibiri mumajuru yose no kw’Isi ni vy’Imana, n’abari iwe ntibishima mukuyi senga kandi ntibaruha"
  21,20,Bayininahaza ijoro n’umutaga kandi ntibadebukirwa
  21,21,Canke baronse izindi Mana kw’Isi bakurikira
  21,22,"Nkiyo hobayeho iyo mw’Ijuru no kw’Isi izindi Mana atari Imana y’ukuri, ntankeka ayo majuru n’Isi yari kwononekara, mugabo Imana irisukuye, Umuremyi w’inyegamo yayo hamwe n’ivyo bayihayagiza ko"
  21,23,Imana ntibazwa ivyo ikora mugabo ibiremwa bantu bose nibo bazobazwa
  21,24,"Canke bafashe aho bofashe izindi Mana nk’Imana y’ukuri, wewe vuga uti:- nimuzane ivyemezo vyanyu kuko ivyo ndababwira n’icibutso c’abari kumwe nanje, hamwe nabamweho imbere yanje, mugabo benshi muribo ntabumenyi bw’ukuri bafise, kuri ivyo ntibavyitayeho"
  21,25,"Ntawe ntitwa rungitse imbere yawe intumwa iyariyo yose mugabo twaramweretse yuko atayindi Mana isengwa atari jewe gusa, rero nimunsenge"
  21,26,"N’abahakanyi b’Imana bavuga bati:- nyene imigisha myinshi yigiriye ikibondo, Imana irisukuye ahubwo abo bamarayika n’abashumvyi b’Imana bafise iteka ntangere"
  21,27,"Ntibayitanguza ko ijambo, nabo bakorera kw’itegeko ryayo"
  21,28,"Niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibiri imbere yabo hamwe n’ibiri inyuma yabo, nabo Bamarayika ntibasabira uwariwe wese ku Mana atari uwo Imana yemereye ivyo bisabisho vyiwe, nabo kubera ukuyitinya baragamburuka"